Business Summary


Manufactures and supplies consumable productsXerium Technologies, Inc. engages in manufacturing and supplying consumable products used in the production of pulp, paper and paperboard, nonwoven products, bulding products and other specialty applications.It operates through the following business segments: Machine Clothing and Roll Covers.The Machine Clothing segment represents the manufacture and sale of synthetic textile belts used to transport paper along the length of papermaking machines.The Roll Covers segment represents the manufacture and refurbishment of covers used on the steel rolls of a papermaking machine.Xerium Technologies was founded in 1976 and is headquartered in Youngsville, NC.Number of employees : 2 950 persons.
 





