 The Company paid cash of $1,205 during 2006 related to this acquisition and made the final payment
in June 2007. The acquisition was accounted for under the purchase method of accounting and, accordingly, PMAs results of operations have been included in the Companys consolidated statements of operations from the date of acquisition.
  
